# Templates

## Singles → content shells

| Root template | Content part |
|---------------|--------------|
| `single-bachelor.php`, `single-master.php` | `template-parts/content/content-single-offer.php` |
| `single-postgraduate.php`, `single-mba.php` | `template-parts/content/content-single-pg-mba.php` |
| `single-courses.php` | `content-single-courses.php` |
| `single-exams.php` | `content-single-exams.php` |
| `single.php` | `content-single-aktualnosci.php` or `content-single.php` + optional `flexible-content/sections/{layout}` |

## Page templates (root)

`front-page.php`, `page-template-offer.php`, `page-template-prices.php`, `page-template-faq.php`, `page-template-contact.php`, `page-template-cadre.php`, `page-template-quiz.php`, `page-template-ranking-ela.php`, `page-template-aktualnosci-archive.php`, `page-template-open-day.php`, `page-template-thank-you.php`, `page-kreowanie-przestrzeni.php`, `page-porownanie-kierunkow.php`, `page-portfolio-sprawdzian.php`, `page-projekty-i-pracownie.php`, `page-katalog-kierunkow.php`, `page-studiuj-to-co-cie-kreci.php`, `page-zasady-rekrutacji.php`, `page-rankingi.php`, `page.php`.

**Front page sections (order):** hero-slider → counter → main title → **decision-today** (static PHP + WPML; layouts `cards` + `compact` for comparison) → offers sliders → home-rankings → …

## LP landing pages

### Seria „Dopasuj studia do siebie” (~10 stron)

Każda LP = **osobny szablon** (nie flexible builder), własny SCSS w `assets/src/scss/pages/_{slug}-page.scss`, ACF JSON w `acf-json/group_{key}.json` z location `page_template` = `page-{slug}.php`.

| Plik | Rola |
|------|------|
| `page-{slug}.php` | Szablon strony; `require` → `configure/lp-defaults/{slug}/fields.php` |
| `configure/lp-defaults/merge.php` | Wspólny `akademiata_lp_merge_defaults()` (ACF nadpisuje, puste repeatery = defaults) |
| `configure/lp-defaults/{slug}/content.php` | Domyślna treść z HTML mockupu (`return [...]`) |
| `configure/lp-defaults/{slug}/fields.php` | `{slug}_defaults()` + `{slug}_fields()` |

**Dopasuj studia:** Kreowanie przestrzeni, Porównanie kierunków, Portfolio i sprawdzian, Projekty i pracownie, Katalog kierunków.

### Seria „Studiuj to, co Cię kręci”

Ten sam wzorzec plików. Pierwsza: **Studiuj to, co Cię kręci** — `page-studiuj-to-co-cie-kreci.php` (LP 02.1, studia I stopnia).

### Seria rekrutacji

**Zasady rekrutacji** — `page-zasady-rekrutacji.php` (kompletny hub rekrutacji: ścieżki PL/zagranica, terminy, dokumenty, pliki, kontakt, FAQ). Prefix ACF: `rekr_`.

## `partials/` vs `template-parts/`

| Folder | Use for |
|--------|---------|
| `partials/` | Site chrome, cards, filters, offer nav — `header.php`, `footer.php`, `card_post*.php`, `nav_single_offer.php`, `filter_side.php` |
| `template-parts/` | Content shells and sections — `content/*`, `single-offer/section_*.php`, `prices/calculator.php`, `front-page/hero-slider.php`, `front-page/home-rankings.php` |
| `template-parts/.../partials/` | Feature-scoped fragments (e.g. `pg-mba/partials/`) |

Load via `get_template_part()` or `locate_template('partials/header.php', true, true)`.

## Bachelor/master sections (dynamic loop)

From `content-single-offer.php`: `section_why_study`, `section_student_testimonials`, `section_after_studies`, `section_after_graduation`, `section_for_you_if`, `section_study_program`, `section_tuition_fees`, `section_recruitment_rules` under `template-parts/single-offer/`.

## ACF in templates

- Top of templates: `get_fields()` → `set_query_var('acf_fields', $acf_fields)`.
- **Front page:** `acf-json/group_front_page.json` (`Front: Page`) — tab **Decyzja na dziś** → group `decision_today` (layouts `cards`|`compact`; defaults `configure/front-page-defaults/decision-today/`). Tab **Rankingi** → group `home_rankings`.
- Options pages: Theme Settings (Header, Footer, contacts) registered in `configure/configure.php`.
- Components: `render_acf_component($type, $data)` → `acf-components/acf-{type}.php`.

## Shell

`header.php` / `footer.php` → `partials/header.php`, `partials/footer.php`.
